  "dialogue.settlements.generic.idle.1": "今天这小风吹得，还挺舒服的",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.idle.2": "事儿多着呢，不过现在先歇会儿",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.idle.3": "*小声哼着调子*",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.idle.4": "希望铁傀儡盯紧点",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.idle.5": "这天气，适合出去溜达溜达",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.idle.6": "村里又是安稳的一天",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.idle.7": "外出小心点哦",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.idle.8": "先喘口气，歇一歇",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.idle.9": "不知道流浪商人今天带了啥",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.idle.10": "今儿天气真不错",

  "dialogue.settlements.generic.work.1": "太阳下山前还有一堆活呢",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.work.2": "我那颗绿宝石放哪儿去了？",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.work.3": "忙啊，真忙啊…",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.work.4": "干一天，赚一颗绿宝石",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.work.5": "停不下来，我正顺手呢",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.work.6": "活儿总是干不完",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.work.7": "差不多该回去干活了",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.work.8": "这一批马上就弄完",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.work.9": "还得再打磨打磨…",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.work.10": "时间就是绿宝石",

  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.work.1": "你瞧这些鸡，长得真漂亮呀",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.work.2": "脚下注意点，那可是刚翻好的地！",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.work.3": "今天这土看着真肥",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.work.4": "得赶紧把这些胡萝卜拔了",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.work.5": "今晚要是下点雨就好了",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.work.6": "那些鸡最好别来啄我的种子",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.work.7": "还剩几垄地要锄",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.work.8": "这骨粉还真管用",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.work.9": "得赶在太阳落山前干完",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.work.10": "杂草，哪儿都是杂草…",

  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.idle.1": "新翻的泥土味儿，真带劲",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.idle.2": "歇一小会儿，腰有点酸",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.idle.3": "就这么瞅着地里的麦子，心里就踏实",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.idle.4": "这季收成不错",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.idle.5": "堆肥桶是不是快满了？",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.idle.6": "你瞧见这季的收成没？",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.idle.7": "现在要是来场雨就舒服了",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.idle.8": "方圆百里，就我这庄稼最好",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.idle.9": "呼，该伸伸腰了",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.idle.10": "天大的活也等我喘口气再说",

  "dialogue.settlements.nitwit.idle.1": "啥？",
  "dialogue.settlements.nitwit.idle.2": "啊？快天黑了吗？该睡了吧？",
  "dialogue.settlements.nitwit.idle.3": "呃… 我刚才要干啥来着？",
  "dialogue.settlements.nitwit.idle.4": "我绿衣服丢了… 哦，我穿着呢",
  "dialogue.settlements.nitwit.idle.5": "*大大地打了个哈欠*",
  "dialogue.settlements.nitwit.idle.6": "我喜欢看云飘来飘去",
  "dialogue.settlements.nitwit.idle.7": "你有面包吗？",
  "dialogue.settlements.nitwit.idle.8": "太困了，脑子转不动",
  "dialogue.settlements.nitwit.idle.9": "草地软乎乎的…",
  "dialogue.settlements.nitwit.idle.10": "要不我去敲下钟？",

  "dialogue.settlements.generic.panic.1": "快跑！",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.panic.2": "救命！",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.panic.3": "别过来！",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.panic.4": "啊啊啊！",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.panic.5": "救救我们！",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.panic.6": "他们打过来了！",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.panic.7": "赶紧撤！",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.panic.8": "别让它们抓到我们！",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.panic.9": "小心！",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.panic.10": "铁傀儡去哪儿了？！",

  "dialogue.settlements.generic.meet.1": "哟，大伙儿都在呢？",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.meet.2": "隔壁村有啥新鲜事吗？",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.meet.3": "*吃瓜中*",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.meet.4": "跟你聊聊挺好",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.meet.5": "今天开张没？赚了几个子儿啊？",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.meet.6": "天天见，你这老脸我都看腻歪了~",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.meet.7": "哎，你听说了吗？隔壁村那谁…",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.meet.8": "去井边歇会儿？",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.meet.9": "来来来，都靠过来",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.meet.10": "今天可真够忙的",

  "dialogue.settlements.generic.morning.1": "早啊！",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.morning.2": "太阳出来了，该干活了",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.morning.3": "新天新气象",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.morning.4": "昨晚睡得还行吗？",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.morning.5": "吃了么？来点煎饼？",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.morning.6": "这就天亮了？我还没睡够呢…",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.morning.7": "今天又是干劲满满的一天！",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.morning.8": "谢天谢地天亮了，昨晚外头那僵尸叫了一宿",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.morning.9": "*打哈欠* 早啊",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.morning.10": "大早上的村子里真清静",

  "dialogue.settlements.generic.evening.1": "瞅瞅，这太阳都快落山喽",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.evening.2": "得嘞，收摊收摊",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.evening.3": "差不多该睡了",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.evening.4": "黑灯瞎火的，外头可不安全",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.evening.5": "晚上好",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.evening.6": "忙忙活活的，这一天过得可真快",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.evening.7": "站了一整天，这老腰老腿都有点麻了…",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.evening.8": "都麻溜回屋！门窗可千万得锁死了啊！",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.evening.9": "差不多了，赶快各回各家吧",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.evening.10": "星象不错，今晚估摸着能睡个安稳觉",

  "dialogue.settlements.generic.rest_day.1": "今天不用干活，真舒坦",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.rest_day.2": "这天气正适合歇着",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.rest_day.3": "总算能放松一下了",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.rest_day.4": "今天我一根手指头都不想动",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.rest_day.5": "就在村里随便转转",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.rest_day.6": "啥也不干，完美的一天",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.rest_day.7": "休息得还舒服吗？",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.rest_day.8": "*摸鱼中*",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.rest_day.9": "啊，清静",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.rest_day.10": "*打哈欠* 待会儿高低得补个觉",

  "dialogue.settlements.generic.zombie_sighted.1": "僵尸！",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.zombie_sighted.2": "小心，亡灵来了！",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.zombie_sighted.3": "铁傀儡，来这边！",

  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.rest_day.1": "今天就让地自己喝水吧",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.rest_day.2": "庄稼明天再管也不迟",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.rest_day.3": "坐着看麦子晃来晃去，也挺好",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.rest_day.4": "农民也得有一天不用晒太阳",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.rest_day.5": "今天不锄地，也不播种",

  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.zombie_sighted.1": "离我的庄稼远点，你这怪物！",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.zombie_sighted.2": "僵尸踩田啦！",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.zombie_sighted.3": "快保护庄稼，别让那东西糟蹋了！",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.zombie_sighted.4": "别进麦田！",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.zombie_sighted.5": "它踩到胡萝卜了！",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.zombie_sighted.6": "守住田地！",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.zombie_sighted.7": "离我的土豆远点！",
  "dialogue.settlements.farmer.zombie_sighted.8": "我漂亮的耕地，全毁了！",

  "dialogue.settlements.generic.idle.cured.1": "我现在闻到腐肉味就受不了",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.idle.cured.2": "那瓶虚弱药水… 灌下去时烧得慌，但好歹是把我捞回来了",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.idle.cured.3": "我老梦见以前那片黑暗",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.idle.cured.4": "有时候还是觉得身子发沉",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.idle.cured.5": "我这条命，算是金苹果给捡回来的",

  "dialogue.settlements.generic.rest_day.cured.1": "能站在太阳底下，我就知足了",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.rest_day.cured.2": "以前只会到处游荡，现在总算能歇会儿",
  "dialogue.settlements.generic.rest_day.cured.3": "能安安稳稳歇一天，真好",

  "subtitles.settlements.cucco_call": "鸡不祥地啼叫",
  "subtitles.settlements.cucco_fall": "鸡不祥地坠落",

  "action.settlements.chest.waxed": "箱子已涂蜡，村民不会使用它",
  "action.settlements.chest.unwaxed": "箱子已除蜡，村民可以使用它"
}
